description:
Live Traffic, GPS, Coupons, Mileage Tracker, Offline Maps, Voice and More

Beat traffic, find cheap gas price options easily, get coupons for discounts near you, track and export your  miles, share your travel details and discover local places all with AT&T Navigator.

NEW! Discover Local Deals:
Get local discounts for nearby restaurants, businesses, services and more with our Coupon feature. Find deals in your neighborhood or when you travel the US, and redeem straight from your device. (Participating merchants are responsible for all coupon redemptions thru this app.)
NEW! Track Your Miles:
Keep track of your trips with Mileage Tracker. Once activated, the app keeps track of your miles - even when it’s not running - and lets you categorize and export them for your expenses.
Beat Traffic: 
Outsmart traffic no matter where you’re headed with more than 100 million real-time traffic sources. Get traffic updates, GPS-enabled multi-route recommendations, one-touch traffic avoidance, speed limit notifications, traffic camera alerts and more.

Find New Favorite Places:
With more than 142 million local reviews and ratings from Yelp® and TripAdvisor®, AT&T Navigator will be your trusted guide to let you explore your city with detailed maps and recommendations.

SUBSCRIPTION CHARGES & OPTIONS
Must have an AT&T mobile phone number and eligible data plan to subscribe. Phone’s internal memory space needed for downloadable maps feature. 

New to AT&T Navigator? Try AT&T Navigator for free* for the first 30 days and enjoy a robust set of navigation features. Unless cancelled, at the end of the 30-day period your account will automatically be billed $9.99 per month. You may cancel at any time. See Subscription Cancellation & Changes for additional information.

Save over $40 with AT&T Navigator Annual Subscription for $69.99 /year. Free 30-day period is not available with the annual subscription offer. 

A free*, limited features version of AT&T Navigator called Basic Maps is available after you download the AT&T Navigator app. 
*Data & messaging rates may apply for app download & usage.

SUBSCRIPTION CANCELATION & CHANGES
You may cancel any time by going to http://www.att.com/mobilepurchases or calling 1.800.331.0500. 
To cancel your AT&T Navigator Annual Subscription and receive a refund, you must cancel within 30 days from the application activation date.
CONTACT US
We want to keep hearing what you love about the app and what we can do to make it even better for you.

Send your comments to support@telenav.com, Subject: AT&T Navigator for iPhone.

Monthly subscription is $9.99/mo. and may be cancelled at any time.  Annual subscription is $69.99 and only can be canceled within the first 30 days. You may cancel at att.com/mobilepurchases or by calling 800.331.0500 (or 611 from your mobile phone).  Basic Maps option is avail. w/no monthly subscription charge. Data & messaging rates may apply for app download & usage.  Compatible phone w/elig. data plan req’d. Phone’s internal memory space is needed to use offline maps feature. App may use your personal info, including location. This use is governed by AT&T’s Privacy Policy found at att.com/privacy. AT&T is not responsible for any third party content and services including coupons. Participating merchants are solely responsible for the processing and redemption of coupons and related offers. Other charges & restr’s may apply. Visit att.com/navigator for add’l terms & conditions.   
AT&T Services, Inc. Web Site Application License Agreement
What's New in Version 4.6
> Coupons: Find discounts for nearby local businesses or when you travel in the US.
> Mileage Tracker: Log and track your miles for reimbursement or tax purposes,  even when the app is turned off.
> Change Origin: Get directions to your destination from your current location, or change your point of origin.

Note: Continued use of GPS running in the background can dramatically decrease battery life.
